00:35:09.120 --> 00:35:11.960
One is exposed to sign
language and the other is not.

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:14.000
We see the success, they
graduate, have a job,

00:35:14.000 --> 00:35:19.040
and are able to take off, while the
other one continues to struggle.

00:35:19.040 --> 00:35:22.400
And that video really
emphasizes the importance

00:35:22.400 --> 00:35:25.040
of early language exposure.

